{"tid":1771576,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【好文整合】我哋未贏架！有冇做齊呢十樣嘢？","createTime":"2019-12-06T03:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T05:41:50.000Z","uid":137109,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"02b1db9c6ecf2b62cd1a1fb2e62915a9a40d7363","tid":1771576,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T03:28:17.000Z","msg":"遊行以外，其實大把嘢等住我哋做：<br />\n<br />\n所有人<br />\n1. 說服身邊人轉軚：區選民意64比，打破嘅唔止係保皇黨嘅壟斷，<br />\n更加證明咗主流一直企喺我地一邊，但留意<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">游離／中立所剩無幾</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n1+1&gt;2 原則：在於每人要去說服身邊一個人轉軚（esp. 淺黃／藍、因自私而轉咗立場嘅人）；<br />\n變相多個同路人，少個敵人。做到呢樣唔容易，但成功嘅話可以翻盤。<br />\n<br />\n睇睇呢個post 有時<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">說服人技巧&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;hard facts</span><br />\n簡單啲講要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">對準人嘅特點</span></span><br />\neg. 需要尊重+被聆聽；你可以俾佢講先，扮尊重/聆聽 --&gt; 聽完意見後可以話唔少人都會好似你咁諗，不過咁樣諗未必全面，可以從其他角度睇。。。<br />\n<br />\n目的係用尊重嘅態度軟化咗理性溝通嘅隔閡，帶佢哋走返入你嘅世界，<br />\n再補足Knowledge，比佢哋知 我哋爭取緊嘅嘢同佢有關係<br />\n<br />\n［文宣要新方向］藍絲可能係我地間接造成<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1757581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1757581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n文宣:<br />\n2. 毋忘初心: 走一轉連儂牆，現況係側重咗狗暴而忽略政治立論/五大訴求，<br />\n中哂正苦下懷；推班condom仔做代罪羔羊<br />\n警暴, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">抗爭正當性應該並重！</span></span> 同時注意用詞，我哋用嘅係武力以唔係暴力 （<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">止戈為武！！！！！</span></span></strong>狗先叫暴力！！！）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">「你想要甚麼？你的願景是甚麼？為何我要支持？」</span></span><br />\nSharon Hom 香港自治現況：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FeMm92zhQ6Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFeMm92zhQ6Q&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScAVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=a399ac1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FeMm92zhQ6Q</a><br />\n(可以再講一啲被扭曲嘅概念：<br />\n如政府 &mdash;&gt; 有民意授權，問責制保障而行使權力<br />\n而非任意莽為不受監察<br />\n法治 &mdash;&gt; 高官與狗犯罪，知法犯法更要受罰而唔可以走數<br />\n一般人應由無罪假定原則保護，<br />\n退一萬步都係一人做事一人當，黑衫=暴徒其實係洗腦Tactics)<br />\n<br />\n和理非<br />\n3. 平時當然<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">支持黃色經濟圈 </span></span>咪再食元氣！比啲骨氣！<br />\n和你eat: <br />\nApple: <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%A0eat/id1483085409\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2F%25E5%2592%258C%25E4%25BD%25A0eat%2Fid1483085409&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScAVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=5bfb5578\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E5%92%8C%E4%BD%A0eat/id1483085409</a><br />\nAndroid: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.woleieat&amp;hl=zh_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.woleieat%26hl%3Dzh_HK&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScAVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=a732c9d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.woleieat&amp;hl=zh_HK</a><br />\n<br />\n4. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">落場掩護勇武撤退</span></span>，唔好一走了之；無gear都可以係哨、街坊， 反包圍被截查嘅人<br />\n--&gt;拖時間比手足離開 可以換衫融入人群<br />\n<br />\n勇武: <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">換裝黑外套+街坊衫！！！</span></span><br />\n5. 相信背後和理非 事前睇熟地形 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勇武只係手段而非最終目的，<br />\n盡早完成目標eg.裝修／交通燈；Set時間退場(eg. 7pm)混入人群</span> <br />\n<br />\n區議會:<br />\n6. 監察你嗰區有冇請手足 做好地區工作去深耕細作? <br />\nSend比你個區嘅區議員:<br />\n區諾軒提醒：<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/未覺池塘春草夢%E1%85%A0階前梧葉已秋聲-時刻警惕-07-年慘痛教訓/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%9C%AA%E8%A6%BA%E6%B1%A0%E5%A1%98%E6%98%A5%E8%8D%89%E5%A4%A2%25E1%2585%25A0%E9%9A%8E%E5%89%8D%E6%A2%A7%E8%91%89%E5%B7%B2%E7%A7%8B%E8%81%B2-%E6%99%82%E5%88%BB%E8%AD%A6%E6%83%95-07-%E5%B9%B4%E6%85%98%E7%97%9B%E6%9