an style=\"color: brown;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Cut哂所有NGO捐款 </span></strong></span>(Amnesty, Green Peace除外)<br />\n去幫更有需要資金嘅機構: <a href=\"https://t.me/HKersFund\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKersFund&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScAVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=b123d0bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKersFund</a> ； 如本土研究社，傳真社，星火<br />\n<br />\n10.<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>[img][img] 唔好善忘 唔好麻木[/img][/img]</strong></span></span> 繼續撐落去 終有一日可以除罩相見<br />\n有橋出橋 有力出力 eg 連儂牆/Twitter/寄信<br />\n<br />\n寄信／聖誕卡畀手足： <a href=\"https://t.me/s/youarenotalonehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fs%2Fyouarenotalonehk&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScAVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=b7152ff8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/s/youarenotalonehk</a>  <br />\nTwitter: tg @TwitterHelpBot<br />\n目錄：<a href=\"https://t.me/hongkongindex\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhongkongindex&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScAVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=fd0632f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hongkongindex</a><br />\n<br />\n老土都要講句 不分化不割席係我哋走到依家嘅大原則 不分和勇 大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12be138f461c34ed3d1517d7a4fe8ab4708a509b","tid":1771576,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T03:29:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cXiy6xU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcXiy6xU.jpg&h=f54faec9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b52c4b0d8fa4bee2b7e929bb6ee4a6ed16e90564","tid":1771576,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T03:31:21.000Z","msg":"幫幫手推，見到熱門Post好似無晒鬥志，感覺以為已經贏咗"},{"pid":"8bd60ba0c2a5ce93329a326bc988771db59ab35f","tid":1771576,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T03:33:26.000Z","msg":"推 1/100"},{"pid":"c973349b